Clough Ltd.


                  Clough Ltd. operates as an engineering and construction contracting company. It offers engineering, onshore and offshore construction, near shore marine, commissioning, brown fields. The company was founded by John Oswald Clough in 1919 and is headquartered in West Perth, Australia.                




